<h2><a href="http://tomoyo.sourceforge.jp/1.8/index.html.en">Fully equipped version (1.x series)</a></h2>

<p><a href="http://tomoyo.sourceforge.jp/1.7/index.html.en">1.7.x documentation</a> (old stable)</p>
<p><a href="http://tomoyo.sourceforge.jp/1.8/index.html.en">1.8.x documentation</a> (current)</p>

<p>This version supports many distributions using 2.4 and 2.6 kernels. Although it requires compilation of a patched kernel, it offers full MAC functionality (for files, network, capabilities, environment variables etc.). It can also be used alongside other MAC implementations (e.g. SELinux, SMACK, AppArmor).</p>

<p>Use this version if your priority is to obtain the most out of TOMOYO Linux and the MAC functionality available.</p>

